Architecture: The TecX LM Transformer

Our model uses a Decoder-Only Transformer architecture optimized for scientific logic.
Rotary Positional Embeddings (RoPE): Better handles long-form mathematical proofs.
FlashAttention-3: Hard-coded for H100/B300 memory speed.
Custom BPE Tokenizer: 32k vocabulary size. It treats 8.854e-12 as a single semantic unit, preventing "math drift" during inference.

The Data Pipeline "Gold Standard"
We do not use raw web scrapes. Our data undergoes a Triple-Filter Process:
Language Filter: Removes non-English scientific text.
Complexity Filter: Discards text below a collegiate physics level.
LLM-Judge: A Llama-3-70B model scores every paragraph for "Scientific Integrity." Only scores > 0.85 are included in the pre-training set.

